1. Install anaconda python
https://www.anaconda.com/distribution/

2. Create an environment for MDMR with MDMR.yml file.
conda env create -f MDMR.yml

Note: rpy2 (v2.9) is sensitive to the versions of numpy and pandas.
They should be numpy==1.15.4 and pandas==0.23.4
MDMR.yml will install these versions.
